 reduced acceptor.\\\"\",\n3:   \"comments\": [],\n4:   \"title\": \"protoporphyrinogen oxidase activity terms\",\n5:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31965\"\n6: }\n\n(End of file - total 6 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"There is currently this tree:\\n\\n```\\nGO:0070818 protoporphyrinogen oxidase activity [no xref]\\n    |__GO:0070819 menaquinone-dependent protoporphyrinogen oxidase activity [EC:1.3.3.4 {source=\\\"skos:broadMatch\\\"}]\\n    |__GO:0004729 oxygen-dependent protoporphyrinogen oxidase activity [EC:1.3.3.4 & RHEA:25576 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}]\\n```\\n\\nEC:1.3.3.4 is \\\"protoporphyrinogen IX + 3 O2 = protoporphyrin IX + 3 H2O2\\\", which matches GO:0004729.\\n- [x] Remove EC:1.3.3.4 xref from GO:0070819.\\n\\nEC 1.3.5.3 is \\\"protoporphyrinogen IX + 3 a quinone = protoporphyrin IX + 3 a quinol\\\" with comment \\\"In the bacterium Escherichia coli it interacts with either ubiquinone or menaquinone, depending on whether the organism grows aerobically or anaerobically.\\\"\\n- [x] Add EC:1.3.5.3 as exactMatch xref on GO:0070819.\\n- [x] Add RHEA:65032 as exactMatch xref on GO:0070819.\\n- [x] Change label of GO:0070819 to more general \\\"quinone-dependent protoporphyrinogen oxidase activity\\\"\\n- [x] Change def of GO:0070819 to match RHEA, \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: protoporphyrinogen IX + 3 a quinone = protoporphyrin IX + 3 a quinol.\\\"\\n- [x] Replace GOC xref in def with RHEA:65032\\n\\n\\nRHEA:62000 is \\\"protoporphyrinogen IX + 3 A = protoporphyrin IX + 3 AH2\\\"\\n- [x] Add RHEA:62000 as exactMatch xref to GO:0070818 and use as def xref (replace existing GOC xref, keep PMID xref)\\n- [x] Change def of GO:0070818 to \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: protoporphyrinogen IX + 3 acceptor = protoporphyrin IX + 3 reduced acceptor.\\\"\",\n  \"comments\": [],\n  \"title\": \"protoporphyrinogen oxidase activity terms\",\n  \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/