{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778978849313,"sessionID":"ses_1cc993ecdffe3y4dc63JDVUGDT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"skill","callID":"call_XjE9Otb084TCSsx4oWRxLEAK","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"name":"external-term-lookup"},"output":"<skill_content name=\"external-term-lookup\">\n# Skill: external-term-lookup\n\n## Finding terms currently in the import closure:\n\n- Search chebi:\n     - `obo-grep.pl --noheader -r cysteine src/ontology/imports/chebi_import.obo`\n\n## Advanced queries over GO\n\nYou can use OAK commands with local obo files:\n\n`runoak -i simpleobo:src/ontology/go-edit.obo tree -p i GO:0160022`\n\n## Finding terms in external ontologies not in the import closure\n\nUse `runoak` on the command line using the OLS adapter plus the ontology\n\n`runoak -i ols:chebi search cysteine`\n\nBase directory for this skill: file:///__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/.agents/skills/external-term-lookup\nRelative paths in this skill (e.g., scripts/, reference/) are relative to this base directory.\nNote: file list is sampled.\n\n<skill_files>\n\n</skill_files>\n</skill_content>","metadata":{"name":"external-term-lookup","dir":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/.agents/skills/external-term-lookup","truncated":false},"title":"Loaded skill: external-term-lookup","time":{"start":1778978849294,"end":1778978849311}},"id":"prt_e336701f40015qbT3QErVZ0rWa","sessionID":"ses_1cc993ecdffe3y4dc63JDVUGDT","messageID":"msg_e3366e9630017PbNla8PMgzj1H"}}
